Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:09.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1048,916)}邮件
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.59,0:01:19.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,官方正品高菲高伯挠背器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:19.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The official Goofy Goober back scratcher
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才用了52个盒盖换来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it only cost me 52 box tops
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.55,0:01:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.86,0:01:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.72,0:01:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是挠背器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's not the back scratcher
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.42,0:01:41.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:41.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my arm
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.07,0:01:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种好东西可不能我们独享
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, we shouldn't keep this all to ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该让章鱼哥来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should let Squidward try it out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.13,0:01:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.88,0:01:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Onward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去章鱼哥家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to Squidward's house
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.45,0:01:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去珊迪家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To Sandy's house
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你得看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy, you gotta see this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.72,0:02:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're coming
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're coming
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑猩猩要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The chimps are coming
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.49,0:02:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.97,0:02:12.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:12.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bosses
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.14,0:02:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要过来视察了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're coming for an inspection
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.57,0:02:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连着一周都在没日没夜地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've worked day and night for a week
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果我每样发明都好不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but none of my inventions are any good
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是今天下午前还造不出伟大的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't have a real impressive invention
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by this afternoon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我经费就要被砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they'll cut my funding
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能离开裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll have to leave Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定发明过不少有用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you invented lots of useful things
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个头盔看着就挺伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This helmet looks impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能干什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it do?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴了就能跟坚果对话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It lets you talk to nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What use is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫花生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Peanut
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.95,0:02:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请回答  花生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, Peanut
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.96,0:02:43.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:43.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"It's dark in here"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.77,0:02:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有别的发明吗  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got anything else, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.12,0:02:49.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的坚果咖啡机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:49.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's my nuttachino machine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能用任何坚果做出泡沫多的热咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It makes a nice hot, frothy cup of any nut you choose
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后是我的全自动胡桃夹子机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And lastly, my fully automated nutcracker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:07.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(396,796)}胡桃
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连个简单的胡桃夹子都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't even make a simple nutcracker
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是有点小毛病嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, it's got a few bugs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟派大星可以帮你修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and I'll help you fix it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything'll be fine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只好面对现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just have to face facts
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要离开裤头村  因为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving Bikini Bottom because
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让珊迪就这么离开  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't let Sandy leave, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她老板要找发明  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're looking for an invention, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那咱就开始发明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So let's start inventing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该认真起来了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to get serious, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有新发明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made an invention
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是根可以拿来写字跟画画的棍子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a stick that you can draw or write stuff with
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫铅笔  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a pencil, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就发明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's already been invented
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个发明好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a good one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个可以发光的玻璃球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a glass ball that lights up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就可以在黑暗里看见东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can see in the dark
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯泡  早就发明了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Light bulb, already invented
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个发明肯定行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know this one will work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.88,0:04:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发明了个平行宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've invented a parallel universe
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫镜子  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a mirror, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就发明了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's already been invented
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人老是盗我创意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody keeps stealing my ideas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得你那创意挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought it was a pretty good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都发明不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never invent anything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,280)}公交
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无法不辞而别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't leave without a good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但千万别看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But please don't think bad of me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假如我开始哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If'n I start to cry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有不少事物我都很想念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's so many things I'll miss
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从你拥挤的雾都
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From your smoggy, crowded city
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再到蜇人的水母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To your stingin' jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里充满着不少事物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This town is filled with many things
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我样样都很爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That I've come to love
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从地上飞行的鸟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From the birds that fly upon the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再到空中的花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the flowers up above
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一点也不愿离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I really hate to go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为这一切当中我最想念的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause the things I'll miss the most of all
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我认识的好朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are the friends I've come to know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真为自己感到羞愧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这么快就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gave up too quickly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要给珊迪的老板造出神发明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll build Sandy's bosses an invention so amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他们一辈子都非给珊迪经费不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they'll give Sandy funding forever
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,780)}汽水
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've done it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们造出了全世界史上最伟大的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We created the greatest invention
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the world has ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, they're here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.25,0:05:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:05:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's bosses
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就因为他们  我们才忙活一下午发明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The reason we spent all afternoon inventing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day, gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给大家介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是珀西教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Professor Percy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是果酱博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Dr. Marmalade
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听候差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At your service
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是雷金纳德巨头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is Lord Reginald
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.23,0:06:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Charmed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个讲话真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys talk funny
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多说一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say more words
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.67,0:06:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是树屋企业有限公司董事会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are the board of directors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of Tree Dome Enterprises Limited
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前来视察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we are here to ascertain
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇克斯小姐的发明是否达标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if Miss Cheek's inventions are up to snuff
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.33,0:06:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪的科学知识造福了这里所有居民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, everyone in town has benefited
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from Sandy's scientific knowledge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪出现以前  我瘦不拉几
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before Sandy showed up, I used to be a scrawny weakling
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那时候很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I used to be dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quite
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问您尊姓大名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And whom do I have the pleasure of addressing?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是派大星教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I am Professor Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Professor?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星博士加教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doctor Professor Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别理他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实习生是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know how interns are
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇克斯小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is Miss Cheeks?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她随时都会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She should be back any moment
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为她跑路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought she ran away
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就因为她什么都不会发明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because she couldn't invent anything
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我派大星博士加教授先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Doctor Professor Patrick to you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不觉得现在得展示珊迪的发明了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's time to show them Sandy's invention
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星博士加教授先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Doctor Professor Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是免费上班的实习生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the unpaid intern
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do the work
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生们  我可以毫不夸张地说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, I can say without exaggeration
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.43,0:07:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是全宇宙史上最重要的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that this is the most important invention
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the history of the universe
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你们献上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全自动挠背机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Automatic Back Scratcher
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加梳头机加挖鼻机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hair Comber, Nose Picker
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加尤克里里调音机9000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Ukulele Tuner 9000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,958)}派大星博士加教授\N最强
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的科研经费全花在这玩意上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where our research money went?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个全自动挠背机加梳头机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An automatic back-scratcher, hair-combing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加挖鼻机加尤克里里调音机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nose-picking ukulele tuner
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  那话我早听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, I've heard that claim before
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.29,0:07:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敢问这个装置是怎么运行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do we know this contraption works?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来演示一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see a demonstration
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请上前一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step right up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好像不是很注重个人卫生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look like you've been neglecting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your personal hygiene
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定这样安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is safe?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我是博士加教授一样确定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As sure as I'm a doctor professor
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你不觉得该测试一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't you think we should test it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我想的不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not exactly what I had in mind
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雷金纳德巨头  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lord Reginald, are you all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is splendid
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely splendid
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Marvelous
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这机器把我鼻孔里的残渣清理干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This machine has evacuated my nostrils
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of unwanted residue
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a manner most pleasant
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  派大星博士加教授先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good work, Mr. Doctor Professor Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  低级助理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, lowly assistant
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在它在喂我美味的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say, now it's feeding me delicious pudding
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,布丁  我不记得发明里面有布丁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pudding, I don't remember that part of the invention
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器在给我尤克里里调音了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now it's tuning my ukulele
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有那个必要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say, was that necessary?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  你太无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, sir, are impertinent
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.09,0:08:54.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:54.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.27,0:09:00.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雷金纳德巨头  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:00.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lord Reginald, are you all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你那意思是没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, was that a yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星博士加教授先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Doctor Professor Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那声惨烈的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horrible screaming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表示机器运转很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,means that it's working
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望珊迪还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really wish Sandy were here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上车了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All aboard
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无处可去时  这趟车还会带你远走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will this bus take you somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you've got nowhere else to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure does
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这趟车会停逃兵村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We make stops in Quittersville
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孬种镇跟废物堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Failuretown and Loserburg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在耍什么猴戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with all the monkey business?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.77,0:09:43.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:43.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It works
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It works
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雷金纳德巨头  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lord Reginald, are you all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的傲慢似乎被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I seem to have ruptured my pomposity
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该关闭这间树屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We shall commence closure of this establishment
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,立刻执行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实话  我都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I'm beginning to question
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这海底树屋到底有没有经济效益了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the economic benefits of underwater tree domes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说到底也没多大意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't make much sense when you get right down to it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想把你留在裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were trying to keep you in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们的所作所为害你没机会再留了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but all we did was ruin your chances to stay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我本来也快被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was about to be fired anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你尽力帮忙  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for trying to help, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也谢谢你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, too, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我派大星博士加教授先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Doctor Professor Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't push it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要走了  果酱博士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are departing, Dr. Marmalade
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My word
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.30,0:10:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激动了老半天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of this excitement
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得我体内的钾含量都降低了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has drastically reduced my potassium levels
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good gracious
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try it again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.49,0:10:45.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:45.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.77,0:10:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我们找了117年的剥香蕉机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the banana peeler
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we have been searching 117 years for
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  他们为你的胡桃夹子发狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, they're going bananas for your nutcracker
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1088,920)}香 蕉
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇克斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Miss Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must say
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经大大超出了我们的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have exceeded expectations
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然可能我脑袋受重伤  糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It may be the extreme head trauma I've suffered
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.28,0:11:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我要给你签订一份为期20年的合同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I am going to offer you a 20-year contract
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且要涨不少经费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a substantial pay rise
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I accept
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我期望你造出伟大发明  奇克斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I expect great things out of you, Miss Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伟大的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great things
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你可以把你的才华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you could put your talents
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全身心投入全自动投屎机的制造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,toward that automatic poop-throwing machine
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们很长时间都没搞懂那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's eluded us for so long
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.01,0:11:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇迹得一个一个来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One miracle at a time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就只差想办法解决一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the only thing left is to figure out what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个麻烦的装置了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with this infernal contraption
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.81,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&\fsp50}老鬼当家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(233.101,458.667)\frz30.02}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:55.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(506.821,736.667)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(390.583,452.001)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(521.493,700.001)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:58.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(429.344,542)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:58.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106,842)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个该死的幽雾真是可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse this cursed, ghostly fog
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连自己鼻子都快看不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can barely see past me own nose
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me ship
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  道路救援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, roadside assistance?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a bit of a flat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要在什么地方等待救援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My location where I'll be staying?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,商业区还是居民区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Business or residence?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居民区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Residence
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来我家干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in my house?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我船送去修了  只好困在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck here while me ship is being repaired
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,修好之前  我要缠上你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Till then, I'm here to haunt ya
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.97,0:13:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, help
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  一定要救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you have to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家里有有有  有鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a gh-gh-gh, a ghost in my house
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我得跟你说多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, how many times do I have to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.79,0:13:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不相信有鬼  而且我不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in ghosts, and I never liked you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.15,0:13:25.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:25.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.68,0:13:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.09,0:13:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你得救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you've got to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.98,0:13:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是飞天魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Flying Dutch
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,man
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想伤害我的小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare hurt my little Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想摸摸这个小家伙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to pet the little guy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事了  飞天魔鬼不会伤害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, Dutchie's not gonna hurt you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.48,0:13:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢来只上好的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love me a good snail
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放开来吓一吓最爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing better than giving a good scare
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.78,0:14:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't get too comfortable
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:40.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,548)}海草哥麦片
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼  你该不会还要再闹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dutchie, is this gonna be much longer?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不怕啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you freaking out, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都已经住一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you've been here a while
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早看完你所有花招了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen all your tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.66,0:15:29.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想表达什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:29.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道自己大势将去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know when I'm washed up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.52,0:15:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多年以来就只会那老一套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been doing the same material for years
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有年轻小伙才吓得动别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scaring is a young man's game
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候该放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to give up the ghost
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是真不当鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No pun intended
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是说我习惯了  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant that I'm just used to it, that's all
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只是得去吓吓别人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've just got to scare someone other than me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,236)}优惠床垫
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介意我试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mind if I test it out?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  躺得好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this does feel comfortable
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能先失陪一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you excuse me a moment?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.21,0:16:12.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:12.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正式确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's official
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not scary anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的都是什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of talk is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只是状态没以前好了  仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just off your game, that's all
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我得休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I just need a break
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  稍微放个假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take some time off, you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, relax a little
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许还得找个朋友住一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe stay with a friend for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.72,0:16:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住在菠萝屋里  躺在舒服的沙发上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On a comfy couch in a pineapple
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再住得久那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just for a little while longer?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住到我恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Till I get back on me feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,六个月后
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一名  你还
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, champ, how's it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn it up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调大声一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn the knob up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁能想到我们竟然有这么多共同点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who'd guess we have so much in common?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.13,0:17:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜欢泰迪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like teddy bears
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢泰迪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like teddy bears
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜欢小马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like ponies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢小马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like ponies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是婚戒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that a wedding ring?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is going on around here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别那么扫兴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob, don't be a stick in the mud
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面的小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out below
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.76,0:17:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三次还更棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even better the third time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  派对已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All righty, boys, party's over
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该走了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to scoot honey
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼  你是想一辈子瘫沙发上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dutchie, do you want to spend eternity on this couch?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沙发可舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it is comfy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照照镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look in the mirror
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都已经魂不附体了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a ghost of your former self
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但咱要帮你摆脱你那龌龊的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we're going to raise you up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from your squalid condition
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用可视化的材料指引你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through the use of visual aids
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么破玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in barnacles is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自我觉醒之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A journey into self-awareness
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The power within
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快从沙发上站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get off of that couch
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿好衣服  飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and into your clothes, Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该要认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to get serious
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先从简单的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start you off easy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得自己能吓倒那个老太婆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think you can take that old lady down there?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓她可太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scaring her is too easy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是我认识的飞天魔鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that's the Flying Dutchman I know
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就去把空谈化为行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see you put those words into action
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.88,0:19:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problemo, compadre
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朗尼  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lonnie, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.28,0:19:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  不祥的飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Tis I, the ominous Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朗尼  有种好用的新产品叫做牙膏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lonnie, there's this great new product
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,called toothpaste
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该用用看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you should try it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,408)}健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.89,0:19:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hit it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  看看你的胸肌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude, look at your pecs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're phenomenal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身子可真硬朗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Truly a hard body
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这二头肌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at those guns
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.03,0:19:51.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:51.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now he's got him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的背阔肌有些松弛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My latissimus dorsi has gone flabby
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得上划船练习架了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to get to a rowing machine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像就是吓不到人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to scare anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.70,0:20:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能大家都再也不相信鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe people just don't believe in ghosts anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚给了我解决你所有问题的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you just gave me the answer to all your problems
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,goblins
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愧疚感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,guilt trip
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you called me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不给你妈打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you called your mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥很爱妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squiddums loves his mama
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你干嘛不给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call me then?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.80,0:20:56.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛不给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:56.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛不给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说你不相信鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard you don't believe in ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.44,0:21:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As in the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上根本没有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No such things
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No such thing as ghosts?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No such thing as ghosts?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不相信有鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't believe in ghosts?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.96,0:21:51.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:51.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.05,0:21:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dutchie, it worked
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又可怕起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got your scare back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且也自信回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And me confidence, too
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.89,0:22:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉我可以狠狠吓别人一跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I feel like I could
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,scare the living criminy out of anybody
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都多亏了有你  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All thanks to you, my boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你的船马上就可以修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And maybe your ship will be repaired soon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我有话要坦白  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have a confession, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的船三个月前就修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My ship's been done for three months now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟你当室友可真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it was nice rooming with ya
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.50,0:22:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你留了点小小的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I left you a little something something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for all your trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要去摧毁更多灵魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's high time for me to ruin more souls
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.55,0:22:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good ol' Dutchie
